# ── NOTE: The following are KEPT in GitHub (not ignored) ──
# data/patients.csv        ← your custom dataset
# src/etl_pipeline.py      ← ETL pipeline
# src/analysis.py          ← analysis script
# src/queries.sql          ← SQL queries
# output/charts/*.png      ← generated charts
# dashboard.html           ← live dashboard
# report/Project_Report.docx ← word report
# requirements.txt         ← dependencies
# README.md                ← project overview
